Interface QueryFactory<T,​F>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of connection queries are made for.
    F - The type of filters that make up the queries.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LdapQueryFactory, QueryFactory
    public interface QueryFactory<T,​F>
